  "title": "Project Engineer #66218",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Design & Manufacture of Material Handling Systems</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Project Engineer</strong></li><li>Working Location: Gul Circle (Transportation provided)</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Mon – Fri, 8.30am – 5.30pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary up to $5,000 + HP Allowance + VB</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Manage and execute all phases of project delivery, encompassing engineering, scheduling, cost control, coordination, and on-site supervision.</li><li>Prepare, submit, and keep track of all necessary project documentation and engineering records.</li><li>Actively monitor project execution for timeliness and quality, promptly addressing and expediting any issues that arise to maintain progress.</li><li>Coordinate with clients, subcontractors, consultants, and other related parties to ensure project specifications are met.</li><li>Oversee the work performed by contractors to confirm adherence to quality standards and project requirements.</li><li>Ensure customer satisfaction with the product delivered and the services provided</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Diploma in Mechanical Engineering or equivalent or with at least 2 years of relevant experience.</li><li>Candidates without experience are welcome to apply as training will be provided.</li><li>Comfortable with working on weekends</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#66218 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
